<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I macro FK/Disarm together..works GREAT!<p>

high monks often macro FK with the ROTWF, or CF, as the timers are almost even.<p>

I also use /doability for a sense heading+/locate combo..great for giving/recieving directions..I didn;t know you could use the name of the skill though, I been using numbers, (/doability 8, etc)<p>

Never really ahd problems with raising FD, just put 60 points into it and let loose...wish i had done the same for ID, once it's past 50 it goes up regularly, and now is only 20 points behind FD (considering I started training it 20 levels later...)</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
